"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-825291cd-2baf-454e-a302-443171208c2a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-46071606-4141-4793-a543-abf58b86427e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bac9f4c8-2e03-41b7-a347-233febe0e9fd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 종이와 인쇄 색상의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f21e3cc1-a16b-4cd2-81b2-56f8d0a119ac\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-58e5b4f4-0877-42c9-9bcc-d69279b89b94\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제한이 거의 없고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-007cc2df-9d08-4217-8621-871aec24d33b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0084cc68-a2d2-408d-b423-b1b9fa77afb1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">형광색이나 독특한 색상으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-49bb9e6d-a268-4fbb-9b71-1e4f241a05d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-48e9cf2f-1268-4b5a-9b6d-99d1ec019655\" style=\"color:#555555;\">작업이 가능하므로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f8d82d83-7ebd-4d01-860d-3a0eede0c6aa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b49ed9ee-ad33-418c-ab77-eb46bd52c689\" style=\"color:#555555;\">명함 하나로도 독특한 느낌을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-50037a71-f9d7-4cf6-8c22-30fece99a439\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-532662c6-b773-465c-976d-fcf642cc478b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주고 싶을 때 많이 사용합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7094e8d6-15f4-43e6-afbc-afecbe0c6445\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e91216ab-19b5-4ebb-a8bb-8c60f9f3c68b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a14ceff5-9884-4c72-ad30-f313a0206bea\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eef7c3b6-62de-49fa-9aa7-0abd0abc65a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">원래의 실크인쇄의 목적은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4f6ea06b-8583-4456-9aab-61d825b37ddf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0261c211-c82e-431f-817b-8b4499b843ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">판촉물 등 종이가 아닌 지질의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0c5fd427-ea29-435a-b62e-4fb42dfd319e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0484374e-cfe4-4cb5-a299-fb2432c5d3ec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">표면을 인쇄할 때</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2083fae9-54a8-4388-ab3a-eb49bca6cce9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e4f11741-a94f-491e-ae93-379ca50a9014\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사용되는 인쇄 방식입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6e8d923d-1d09-4719-bca0-3e4fe02f9835\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8eddf817-e64a-4f51-a8be-496967c31012\" style=\"color:#555555;\">플라스틱, 철판, 나무 등에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5e60c473-0f35-4117-80c4-80cebef1d8cd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e65af14c-68b0-4026-83d3-0cb31ab21312\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄를 하는 방식으로 많이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-27629213-88b5-4295-b387-c8dcffa5d503\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-030005a8-37b4-433c-8bbe-ea2e6b94e725\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사용되었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-93deef0c-927c-4e5f-8786-17182b6d1e42\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8d3632e9-f6d0-44c1-a250-2e1fb6a634c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a355ffb5-d6d5-4d2e-a292-4e1d00a8afd5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-993aad9d-07bf-4b11-8908-1f1eb6ea1bb6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 요즘은 종이에도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-beaa8b62-ecbf-4657-b03b-049af33af1e5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8cf4174c-0871-49d0-9125-37fe6ce4b8c8\" style=\"color:#555555;\