555;\"><b>내용물 보호가 목적</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-27980ed4-4754-4cc7-ac0d-b80ff94e5bd8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5d3c134f-3c70-4cfa-a458-f1f7f886a94b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2fca8f32-cba3-4cc9-a07e-f8f4c509c8df\" style=\"color:#555555;\">보호 포장용인 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-64dbe272-b26c-4f8d-b172-968fd19e77d6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-de8da569-a79f-43e9-b8d0-0b888f4ab0a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-74ec7e57-4699-42e7-ad40-793b297c5132\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9fad411c-bded-44be-8014-57ae2ddb4944\" style=\"color:#555555;\">셋, 디자인이나 제품이 심플하여</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5b511560-2920-4421-9ec7-763b60afeaa3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3bf396be-57c3-48b9-bfa1-25d2cfd36d8b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>간단한 디자인</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9aea51b-7254-459b-b203-a6defe20a6a8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만으로도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b7422889-e596-4a62-9d59-faa444c58159\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f015f284-c881-4878-ba2c-aae67b916801\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품을 인식할 수 있는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=